{
  "stem": "25209.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Orlova became Polish when the Germans and the Poles did some kind of a deal with Chamberlain and, you know, this-- I don't know who else was in it-- Chamberlain, Roosevelt?",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Who knows?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Anyway, they sat around and they say, you have this bit.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You have this bit.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now leave us alone-- except doesn't work that way.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He just said, we will go on a holiday.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he packed a few things, and we had a car.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he took all these clocks and things, which got us into trouble later on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he packed up part of the shop.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we locked up the house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we said, we're going away on holidays.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we ended up in Krakow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I always used to think it was Warsaw, but it wasn't.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was Krakow because that's where the bombs started falling.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that would have been '39, I suppose.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we, I mean, the refugees were just fleeing, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were rivers of refugees.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then there were rivers of these Polish soldiers that were fleeing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in the middle of this chaos, we met-- ran into my father's apprentice and his two elderly parents.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We're at this teensy-weensy little [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, you know, mom and dad were in the front.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was in the back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And dad, he was very kind-hearted.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He took the two elderly people, stuck them in the back with me, and the boy, Lolac, was standing-- you know the old cars, they had like a step-- he was standing on that and holding on to the top.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that's how we traveled a little-- a little further.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then there was an incident where they were told that the Germans won't, won't hurt the women and children.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They will only hurt the men.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
